REACTION   (79-AU-197(7-N-12,NON),,SIG,,,DERIV)
ANALYSIS   The total reaction cross section was determined from
           the fitting of the optical model.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) The uncertainty was estimated as the
           standard deviation of the sigmaR calculated with the
           OM at different energies, within the energy
           uncertainty of Elab = 70.0+-3.0 MeV.
